SUMMARY:Deadline: Open Call: SIT/PLU Residencies 2027
DESCRIPTION:Open call for SIT/PLU residencies starting January 2027 hosted 
 by Baltan Laboratories. Selected residents receive a €13\,500 artist fee
  (travel excluded) plus a production budget. Each partner institution deta
 ils its specific residency terms\, role\, payment\, production budget and 
 minimum requirements in separate attachments to the general open call. Dea
 dline 31 May 2026\, 23:59 CET.\n\nOrganisation: Baltan Laboratories\nLocat
 ion: Eindhoven\, Netherlands\nAward: €13\,500 artist fee (travel exclude
 d) + production budget\nDuration: Starts January 2027\n\nMore: https://www
 .baltanlaboratories.org/library/open-call-sit-plu-residencies-2027
